To achieve the desired functionality of loading partial views without navigating to a different page, you can utilize AJAX and jQuery. Here's how you can modify the code:

Create a new empty <div> element inside the <div class="col-10 mt-3 admin_second_content"> div. Give it an id, such as "partialViewContainer". This will be the container where the partial views will be loaded.
